-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Pip purse</h3>\n<p><strong>Holds 250 pips</strong></p>\n<p>Carried pips require one inventory slot per 250, barring the first 250, which are carried in your mouseâ€™s pockets.</p>\n<p>Mice in settlements mostly deal in barter and IOUs, and pips can be stored at a bank.</p>","frontmatter":{"slug":"inventory","title":"Inventory"}},"toc":{"edges":[{"node":{"markdown":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Brave mice in a dangerous world","section":"Player rules","slug":"brave-mice-dangerous-world"}}}},{"node":{"markdown":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Make a mouse","section":"Player rules","slug":"make-a-mouse"}}}},{"node":{"markdown":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Inventory","section":"Player rules","slug":"inventory"}}}},{"node":{"markdown":{"frontmatter":{"title":"How to play","section":"Player rules","slug":"how-to-play"}}}},{"node":{"markdown":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Magic","section":"Player rules","slug":"magic"}}}},{"node":{"markdown":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Recruiting help","section":"Player rules","slug":"recruiting-help"}}}},{"node":{"markdown":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Running Mausritter","section":"GM rules and resources","slug":"running-mausritter"}}}},{"node":{"markdown":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Creatures","section":"GM rules and resources","slug":"creatures"}}}},{"node":{"markdown":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Hexcrawl toolbox","section":"GM rules and resources","slug":"hexcrawl-toolbox"}}}},{"node":{"markdown":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Adventure site toolbox","section":"GM rules and resources","slug":"adventure-site-toolbox"}}}},{"node":{"markdown":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Useful tables","section":"GM rules and resources","slug":"useful-tables"}}}}]}},"pageContext":{"title":"Inventory","section":"Player rules","slug":"inventory"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3449107851"],"slicesMap":{}}